hopobject.body: I sing in a choir cheap kamagra with paypal To all the Soros haters, I say, Soros’ charity speaks louder than any hateful remarks. I’m not related to him, nor agree with his liberal agenda. Soros is a self made Billionaire who is doing what all billionaires should do, but don’t. As for the 40 somewhat year difference between him and his wife to be? Why not. He deserves to have what pleases him, regardless of what we think. God bless ya, Soros. You’re a good man.
